## Setup

{% if deps_manager == "pixi" %}
```bash
pixi install
```
{% elif deps_manager == "uv" %}
```bash
uv venv
source .venv/bin/activate  # On Windows: .venv\Scripts\activate
uv pip install -e ".[dev]"
```
{% else %}
```bash
conda create -n {{repo_name}} python={{python_version}}
conda activate {{repo_name}}
pip install -e ".[dev]"
```
{% endif %}

## Training

{% if deps_manager == "pixi" %}
```bash
# Train SAC on Pendulum-v1 (default)
pixi run train

# Train TD3 instead
pixi run train-td3

# Fast debug run (single step, tiny buffer)
pixi run train experiment=debug

# Train on LunarLanderContinuous-v2
pixi run train experiment=lunar_lander

# Override hyperparameters from the command line
pixi run train agent.gamma=0.98 env.normalize_obs=false
```
{% else %}
```bash
# Train SAC on Pendulum-v1 (default)
python src/{{repo_name}}/train.py

# Train TD3 instead
python src/{{repo_name}}/train.py agent=td3

# Fast debug run (single step, tiny buffer)
python src/{{repo_name}}/train.py experiment=debug

# Train on LunarLanderContinuous-v2
python src/{{repo_name}}/train.py experiment=lunar_lander

# Override hyperparameters from the command line
python src/{{repo_name}}/train.py agent.gamma=0.98 env.normalize_obs=false
```
{% endif %}

